begin\": 271, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999997386403607, \"rank\": 2.3335166897010448e-07, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron said he was confident the planned Games ceremony with huge crowds around the Seine, where some 160 boats would set off for a 6 km journey, would be a huge success.\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 340, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_Stadium\", \"score\": 0.9999999907677193, \"rank\": 9.23251695390168e-09, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_Stadium\"}, {\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9975041184149897e-19, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But France, he added, is not naive.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 516, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.095728835922208e-28, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we think there are security risks we will have plan Bs, and even plan Cs,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One option, he said, would be to restrict the ceremony to the central Paris Trocadero square facing the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 708, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.812957116026944e-27, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 714, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trocadero\", \"score\": 0.9609535636685481, \"rank\": 0.040618093571925584, \"text\": \"Trocadero\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trocadero\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trocadero\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another would be to move the event indoors to the Stade de France stadium.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron then tried - and failed - to convince a mother, worried about security risks, to let her son go to the river Seine ceremony.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 832, \"end\": 838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_Stadium\", \"score\": 0.9999999907677193, \"rank\": 9.23251695390168e-09, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_Stadium\"}, {\"begin\": 948, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9975041184149897e-19, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If there is one place where your son will be safe it will be there,\\\" Macron told the mother, who asked her question during a BFM TV and RMC radio interview.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1035, \"end\": 1041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_Stadium\", \"score\": 0.9999999907677193, \"rank\": 9.23251695390168e-09, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_Stadium\"}, {\"begin\": 1091, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFM TV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}, {\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RMC_(France)\", \"score\": 0.9999999895726432, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RMC radio\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RMC_(France)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RMC_(France)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let him go, it's once every 100 years, the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The unconvinced mother responded that she hoped her son would work that day and be unable to attend.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron, who gave his interview from Paris' Grand Palais museum, which has just been refurbished to host the fencing and taekwondo competitions, said he had not changed his mind about swimming in the Seine.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1282, \"end\": 1288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_Stadium\", \"score\": 0.9999999907677193, \"rank\": 9.23251695390168e-09, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_S