\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Newly arrived at Borussia Dortmund, Haaland scored two in the first leg against Paris Saint-Germain and revealed his \\\"Zen\\\" goal celebration, sitting down cross-legged as if meditating.\", \"from\": 4997, \"to\": 5181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mbapp\\u00e9 and PSG won in Paris to advance 3-2 on aggregate score.\", \"from\": 5182, \"to\": 5244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5182, \"end\": 5188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.9954701649286468, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mbapp\\u00e9\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\"}, {\"begin\": 5204, \"end\": 5209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.812957116026944e-27, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last season, in the knockout playoffs in February, Mbapp\\u00e9 scored four times including a hat trick in the second leg as Madrid beat Man City in both games, despite Haaland's two goals in the first leg.\", \"from\": 5246, \"to\": 5446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5297, \"end\": 5303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.9954701649286468, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mbapp\\u00e9\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\"}, {\"begin\": 5365, \"end\": 5371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.693560623109691e-41, \"text\": \"Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/